Package vallibrary.measures.WCSS

Class Summary
WCSSFast The WCSS_Fast class provides an object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Within Clusters Sum of Squares in Fast Mode.
WCSSFastA The WCSS_Fast_Precision class provides an object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Within Clusters Sum of Squares.
WCSSGeneric the WCSS_Generic class provides an object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Within Clusters Sum of Squares.
WCSSGenericA The WCSS_Generic_Precision class provides an object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing WCSS Measure and relative assessment by computing average adjusted rand index.
WCSSHierarchical The WCSS_Hierarchical class provides an object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing WCSS Measure.
WCSSHierarchicalA The WCSS_Hierarchical_Precision class provides an object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing WCSS Measure and relative assessment by computing average adjusted rand index.
WCSSHierarchicalInit The WCSS_Hierarchical_Init class provides an object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing WCSS Measure.
WCSSHierarchicalInitA The WCSS_Hierarchical_Init_Precision class provides an object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing WCSS Measure and relative assessment by computing average adjusted rand index.
